== Phase 1 (GTA01Bv4) ==

400 Phase 1 devices are ready, and 600 more will be ready during the next week. (Around 5th July)

They will be available to order on July 9th.
Details of how to order will follow.
The Neo Base will cost $300, the Neo Advanced will cost $450.

Details of how to order these will follow.

Neo Base -- everything the mobile application developer needs to enjoy
